# CROSS-REQ-01 - Global Opportunity Registry Report

Date: 2026-06-09

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

## Summary

CROSS-REQ-01 established the Axodus Global Opportunity Registry as a local/unversioned portfolio visibility artifact.

The registry consolidates documented opportunities, product candidates, readiness tracks and strategic initiatives across all major Axodus nuclei using the Business L4 lifecycle, product catalog, risk/governance and dependency frameworks.

Final assessment: `GLOBAL_OPPORTUNITY_REGISTRY_ESTABLISHED`

Recommended next request: `CROSS-REQ-02 - Cross-Nucleus Dependency Registry`

