## Registry Methodology

The registry includes only opportunities supported by repository or portfolio evidence.

Primary evidence sources:

- Business L4 framework documents;
- global portfolio status, roadmap, blocker and maturity registers;
- portfolio gated advancement and promotion board reports;
- nucleus status, roadmap, handoff, blocker, validation and maturity assessment files;
- recent Trading, ACS, Dex, Documentation, BBA and Lottery request reports where applicable.

Items mentioned in request context but not supported by documentation were placed under `Unverified / Needs Documentation` rather than official registry entries.

