## Blockers Summary

Portfolio-wide blockers preserved:

- production readiness is not approved;
- root global docs are local/unversioned;
- execution-sensitive opportunities require separate gate reviews;
- treasury, wallet, trading, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payout, lottery payout, ACS provisioning and on-chain writes remain blocked;
- unverified concepts require documentation before registry promotion.

